lead_paragraph: Garbine Muguruza was once again left to sift through the remains of another failed U.S. Open campaign after the third-seeded Spaniard suffered a shock 7-5 6-4 second round upset by unheralded Latvian Anastasija Sevastova on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Muguruza U.S. Open Hopes Dashed on Ashe
